# English-only instructions

Write and edit **contributor-facing** docs in English:

- `AGENTS.md`, `.cursor/rules/`, `harness/`, `evals/`, `plans/`
- harness docs in `docs/` (agent-first, best-practices, ci-cd, evals, telemetry)
- plan templates, PR template, new harness contracts

Do not add Russian (or other non-English) text to these paths. End-user workspace templates under `workspace-examples/` may stay multilingual.
